# Splash artwork is intentionally NOT committed yet (pending licensing
# clearance). It is kept locally so the splash renders during development; the
# app builds and runs without it — the splash pane shows an "image unavailable"
# notice when the asset is absent (see app_register.go / splashscreen.go).
#
# assets/NOTICE (no extension) is committed and is not matched by these globs.
/assets/patronus.png
/assets/*.png
/assets/*.jpg
/assets/*.jpeg
/assets/*.webp
/assets/*.gif
